<br />Are you talking desktop, laptop, netbook, PSP/smartphone-class handheld, or DS-class handheld?
<br />
<br />And how many NES consoles did you plan on emulating at a time? Let's assume you're talking about a nemulator-style menu. A PS1 demo disc needs 12, and a Wii Menu needs 18: 12 for the channels fully on screen, 3 for the ones barely on the left side, and 3 for the ones barely on the right side. (Technically, the PS1 menu is a video and Wii channel banners are sprite animations, but still...)

		

